Script Type: Batch

Description:

    Batch right-click menu script for <NodeName> node. This script was created by Batch Nodes script.

Menu:

    Right-click in batch -> Batch Nodes... -> <NodeName>

Updates:

    v3.10.0 04.04.25
        - Updated to PyFlameLib v4.3.0.

    v3.9.0 01.04.25
